Dialogue: 5,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.46,Default,Mu,0,0,100,,Okay, Apo...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:05.46,0:00:08.71,Default,Mu,0,0,100,,Don't move an inch...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:09.34,0:00:10.85,Default,Mu,0,0,100,,I told you to stay!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.85,0:00:14.45,Default,Hibi,0,0,100,,Apo, stay here, so you can say hello.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.28,Default,Mu,0,0,100,,Why do you listen to Hibito?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.65,Default,Hibi,0,0,100,,Come on, Mu...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.65,0:00:21.84,Default,Mu,0,0,100,,Huh? Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.74,0:00:28.48,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hello, {\i1}Space Brothers{\i0} viewers!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.48,0:00:34.13,Default,Both,0,0,0,,We wish you a happy new year.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.04,0:00:38.39,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,We hope that you will continue...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.86,0:00:43.27,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,...to give your unwavering support...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:43.76,0:00:48.58,Default,Both,0,0,0,,...to this show.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.03,0:00:53.03,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.09,OP,,0,0,0,,I can't get lost in what I'm doing, nothing works out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.63,OP,,0,0,0,,I don't want these endlessly dull days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.88,OP,,0,0,0,,I hope I can move on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.55,OP,,0,0,0,,before the call of freedom drags me away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.72,OP,,0,0,0,,What's your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.51,OP,,0,0,0,,I just want some real courage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.39,OP,,0,0,0,,We all stare doubt in the face, every one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:27.31,OP,,0,0,0,,Isn't the unpredictability of life the fun of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:31.07,OP,,0,0,0,,Devote your life to that dream you can't express
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:34.94,OP,,0,0,0,,Let's go, advance against the wind, our road is long
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:38.95,OP,,0,0,0,,Embrace the pain of it too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:42.91,OP,,0,0,0,,Take a big breath now, and yell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:50.79,OP,,0,0,0,,Big Bang! Chase it without fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:02:00.51,OP,,0,0,0,,I want to dream so badly it amazes me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:09.98,OP,,0,0,0,,There's cowardice in the way of your true wish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:16.03,OP,,0,0,0,,Rip that hot veil aside
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.99,0:02:22.99,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.45,0:02:29.42,title,EpTitle,0,0,0,,{\fad(446,688)\fax-0.15\bord0\blur0.5\c&HEFEAED&\pos(956,527)}#88 Pretty Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:29.42,title,EpTitle,0,0,0,,{\fad(446,688)\fax-0.15\1a&HFF&\blur1.5\bord1\3c&H1C2E3A&\pos(956,527)}#88 Pretty Dog
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.50,0:02:29.00,Default,A,0,0,0,,Support divers are in the water.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.46,Default,A,0,0,0,,All preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.83,0:02:35.09,Default,A,0,0,0,,We will now begin the scheduled training.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.55,Default,B,0,0,0,,Why do we have to be here?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.91,0:02:42.37,Default,C,0,0,0,,Isn't this just normal EVA training?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.06,Default,But,0,0,0,,No, we require your presence here as witnesses.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.15,Default,A,0,0,0,,Okay, send him down.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.15,0:02:49.79,Default,B,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.17,Default,But,0,0,0,,Please watch closely...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.15,0:03:02.28,Default,But,0,0,0,,To see if he can complete this training without any issue.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.24,Default,B,0,0,0,,Issue?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.67,0:03:07.25,Default,C,0,0,0,,He suffers from panic attacks that cause a complete breakdown.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.34,0:03:12.52,Default,B,0,0,0,,If he fails this training, his career is over.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.84,0:03:17.76,Default,C,0,0,0,,Yes, if he fails, it's over.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.31,0:03:19.62,Default,D,0,0,0,,Looking good, Hibito.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.62,0:03:20.88,Default,D,0,0,0,,Stay calm and follow instructions.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.71,0:03:22.72,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.70,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,H-Hey... What is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.71,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,It's completely dark.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.71,0:03:50.06,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.48,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.90,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this part of the test?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.42,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,There's been an accident... Water's entering my helmet!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.50,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Pull me up! Do you read me?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.50,0:04:03.76,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.59,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pull me up...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.25,0:04:49.43,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.43,0:04:53.27,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,C-Could you pull over for a moment?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.21,Default,A,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.44,Default,A,0,0,0,,Are you getting out here?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.55,Default,A,0,0,0,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.70,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,You can go...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.57,0:05:51.36,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has all my hard work been for nothing?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.34,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.55,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let a stupid dream...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.83,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}trigger a panic attack!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.59,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.04,0:06:47.38,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,Someone also left a cosmos here this time last year. {D: NB - this is much less obvious than in the manga, but it is a flashback (the manga chapter began with it, and then circled back around to it--this episode kind of does the reverse)}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.17,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.17,0:06:51.84,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.58,0:06:58.64,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,At first, I was going to leave a rose,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.81,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,but Mu said that was stupid,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.33,0:07:07.32,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,"Brian's an astronaut, so give him a cosmos."
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.47,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,So last year, I started leaving these.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.16,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,Sounds like something he would say.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.04,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Did you leave the yuri lily? {D: NB - okay, I realize that yuri isn't really a kind of lily, but without including both parts, I think the reference to Gagarin a few lines down will be totally confusing}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.79,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,Yeah, I placed it there earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.41,0:07:24.54,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Was that a play on Yuri Gagarin?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.01,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,Certainly not.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.99,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,You helped to introduce me to Ivan...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.70,0:07:42.19,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,And thanks to his unusual methods, I've been recovering.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.86,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.57,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,Then, have you talked to Mutta?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.27,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I haven't told Mu yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.99,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I'm hoping to recover before he finds out.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.89,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.37,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,Before he finds out...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.92,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,Why do you want that?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.49,0:08:04.38,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.68,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.53,0:08:24.59,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,So, did you get a chance to talk to Brian?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.65,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Eh? Brian?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.61,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,When you were visiting his grave.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.22,0:08:37.07,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,O-Oh... I guess, maybe.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.50,0:08:43.62,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you had an attack with all the directors watching,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.87,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}what would you do, Brian?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.77,0:08:56.77,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,When you aren't sure what to do, you can ask Brian for advice,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.60,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,and you'll always get a response.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.06,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,That applied when he was alive,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.48,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,and it still applies now.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.24,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I have to agree.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.90,0:09:19.95,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,The Brian inside me always has a response.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.60,0:09:31.67,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,As an only child, Brian was like an older brother to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.67,0:09:35.30,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Oh, actually, I felt the same way.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.31,0:09:38.02,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,He was like a father...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.91,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Like a brother.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.89,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,When you feel you've hit a wall,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.63,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,you can talk to our big brother.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.58,0:09:53.77,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,He'll probably give you his usual offhand response.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.49,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,But if that still doesn't help,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.95,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,you can talk to your real big brother.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.44,0:10:08.41,Default,Azu,0,0,0,,You have another big brother you can turn to.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.33,0:10:18.75,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I supposed to do next,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.39,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brian?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.34,0:10:29.52,Default,Brian,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hibito...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.52,Default,Brian,0,0,0,,Look at my getup.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.04,Default,Brian,0,0,0,,I'm on vacation for now.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.04,0:10:38.27,Default,Brian,0,0,0,,I'm off to Hawaii for an Elvis concert...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.11,0:10:45.41,Default,Brian,0,0,0,,Looks like there's something bothering you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.18,0:10:48.87,Default,Brian,0,0,0,,Then I have some advice for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.71,Default,Brian,0,0,0,,Before you start asking the dead and God for help,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.09,Default,Brian,0,0,0,,you should look around...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.15,Default,Brian,0,0,0,,Talk to your big brother who's alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.90,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,So you're telling me the same thing...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.82,0:11:26.79,Default,A,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.75,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Hey! I've been waiting for you, Mu.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.22,0:11:34.21,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Huh? You're completely soaked.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.94,0:11:38.16,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Did you ride your bike here?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.97,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I left my bike at NASA.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.35,0:11:47.77,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Well, if you want to know why I'm soaked, it's a long story...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.69,0:11:53.53,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Today, I want to talk.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.94,0:11:55.94,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she's asleep, she's pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.50,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she's awake, she's pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.50,0:12:07.20,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter where she is or with whom she is, she's pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.48,0:12:10.57,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's the Pretty Dog!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.28,0:12:15.25,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pretty Dog is out for another pretty walk.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.73,Default,B,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Pretty Dog.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.30,Default,B,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you headed today?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.97,Default,C,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh! Look at that dog!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.97,0:12:25.02,Default,C,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's wearing a dress to go with that ugly face.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.02,0:12:28.42,Default,C,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks so pretty!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.98,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look at Pretty Dog go...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.58,0:12:37.19,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once again, she's the center of attention!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.46,0:12:42.99,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,We've reached the point where they've made a cartoon about a pug.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.56,0:12:45.16,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Are you happy, Apo?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.52,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.65,0:12:51.16,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Don't sit so close to the TV... You're too close.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.52,0:12:57.08,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, she lives to go on walks!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.33,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll be back right after these messages.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.55,0:13:09.26,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, put on a Pretty Dog headband, and dress to be the center of attention!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.26,0:13:13.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can also get the brand-new Pretty Dog hairbrush and Pretty Dog mirror.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.12,0:13:16.16,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's be pretty!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.78,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.70,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hibito?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.76,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I'm at the Seelook Pub right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.76,0:13:39.06,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't we get a drink together?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.91,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's raining, but would you come out here?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.67,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something I want to talk to you about."
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.16,0:13:52.60,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hibito wants to talk to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.53,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to turn to me for help.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.40,0:14:18.37,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,This is as rare as an annular eclipse.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.72,0:14:21.97,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.09,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,So? What's up?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.55,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.90,0:14:31.24,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure how to explain this...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.43,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Mu,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.52,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,do you know what "PD" stands for?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.63,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,"PD"?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.63,0:14:46.49,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.95,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,You mean Pretty Dog. What about it?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.24,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Not that!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.45,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Huh? That's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.64,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Th-Then it must be...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.30,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Palladium?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.17,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,The chemical symbol is Pd.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.42,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,"Panic disorder."
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.38,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,It's an anxiety disorder.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.20,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.78,0:15:17.31,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Panic disorder?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.62,0:15:26.98,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,That's what I'm currently suffering from.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.70,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,My heartbeat jumps, I get dizzy, and I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.94,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Basically, I freeze in place.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.66,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,In my case,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.93,0:15:45.13,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I suffer panic attacks from wearing a spacesuit in an enclosed area.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.10,0:15:51.09,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,It probably doesn't sound that bad, but it's harder than you'd think.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.64,0:15:54.80,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Wh-When did this start?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.90,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,When I came back to Earth, from the moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.38,0:16:10.96,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,It hasn't gone away since.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.38,0:16:28.21,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I've been removed from active duty.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.05,0:17:01.62,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,So, next week, the directors are making time to watch me take a test.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.39,0:17:06.58,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,This test will decide if I can return to space.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.33,0:17:12.87,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,But in the taxi home, I had a nightmare that triggered an attack.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.01,0:17:26.91,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,As it stands, I don't see how I'll be able to pass the test.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.73,0:17:36.99,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Eat some more.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.55,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'm buying.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.55,0:17:41.08,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Drinks are on me, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.55,0:17:47.25,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Still, this is a surprise.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.90,0:17:51.42,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,You're the last person I'd expect to get PD.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.02,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.13,0:17:58.67,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I mean, you'd expect sensitive people like me to succumb to that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.35,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hey, can I get another?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.31,Default,A,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.12,0:18:07.70,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,But if a carefree guy like you can get it...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.92,0:18:15.69,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,It worries me about how I'm gonna cope.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.64,Default,A,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.64,0:18:22.70,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.38,0:18:26.00,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,If I were in your shoes,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.96,0:18:32.96,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'd probably run away from the test.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.70,0:18:40.78,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,But while a carefree guy like you may worry, you'll go through with it.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.18,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,That's how you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.80,0:18:46.42,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Right now, if I told you to quit, you'd still take the test.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.85,0:18:52.06,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Because deep down, you have things within you that are definite.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.29,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hibito.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.75,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Can I borrow some money?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.75,0:19:18.76,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Seems I'm short.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.18,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Take this umbrella.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.67,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Huh? What about you?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.67,0:19:30.77,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I need to drop by the grocery store on the way home.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.65,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I have the money I borrowed from you...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.97,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Are you worried about getting home?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.41,0:19:40.55,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.86,0:19:48.50,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Oh... That's right, Hibito...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.96,0:19:56.13,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,If you ever feel like you're going to have a panic attack, just say this...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.30,0:20:03.09,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,"Here comes the PD... Pretty Dog!"
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.78,0:20:05.80,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.04,0:20:09.28,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,You're pretty drunk, Mu.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.10,0:20:15.12,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Wait, that'll lodge the image of Pretty Dog in your mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.12,0:20:18.02,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Or the image of Apo's stupid look.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.13,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.82,0:20:29.74,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,You seem to be concerned that you had an attack in a taxi.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.72,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,But I think you should be relieved.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.61,0:20:36.71,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.28,0:20:44.03,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,That means the spacesuit isn't causing the attacks.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.38,0:20:51.57,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,We grew up dreaming about spacesuits.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.67,0:20:57.27,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,The spacesuit is on our side.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.34,Default,A,0,0,0,,Did something good happen, sir?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,You have a big smile on your face.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.34,0:21:26.01,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:26.01,0:21:31.11,Default,A,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're my happiest customer today.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.11,0:21:38.16,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Say, mister...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.89,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Mind if I ask a strange question?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.61,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Do you know what "PD" stands for?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.04,0:21:44.54,Default,A,0,0,0,,"PD"?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:44.54,0:21:47.43,Default,A,0,0,0,,PD would be that...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:47.43,0:21:49.07,Default,A,0,0,0,,panic something.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.73,0:21:51.51,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:52.69,0:21:56.45,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I was talking about "Pretty Dog."
Dialogue: 5,0:22:04.97,0:22:04.97,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:16.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,520)}The starlight illuminates my future, It's wow... truth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:23.07,ED,,0,0,0,,It's 3 AM, and I dream awake
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:26.78,ED,,0,0,0,,With no idea of my future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:32.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,521)}only impatience consumes me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:41.13,ED,,0,0,0,,I have a thorn in my heart that won't allow me to lose to him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:46.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,519)}I'm walking a path of thorns I made for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:51.93,ED,,0,0,0,,But I won't forget the love I found
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:55.64,ED,,0,0,0,,And I won't forget the ones close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:23:01.48,ED,,0,0,0,,I realized you cannot live your life alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:09.15,ED,,0,0,0,,The starlight illuminates my future, and we are all shooting stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:17.20,ED,,0,0,0,,My holy wishes turn all our sad lies into something better
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:20.87,ED,,0,0,0,,Our orbits have gotten separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:25.67,ED,,0,0,0,,but I'm fine if you are close
